title: Сквот
overview: According to the plot, the major guy Max, in search of his sister, ends up in a squat. He thought about coming in for a minute, but he was stuck there for a long time, caught up in a whirlpool of mysterious events. He will meet his neighbors: a drag dealer, a girl punk band, an aspiring actress, a system administrator, a gopnik, a gay man, a migrant worker and other inhabitants of the squat.
